      "FCDO legalization",
      "UAE Embassy attestation",
      "MOFA attestation in the UAE"
    ],
    desc: "UK Degree Attestation generally follows solicitor or notary verification before FCDO legalization."
  },
  {
    id: "usa",
    name: "United States",
